Title: Good Time Boy
Description:
<A very wet gorloc totem rests on the cave floor. How did this even get here?

The niffen love stuff like this. Maybe someone in Loamm will take it off your hands.>
ObjectivesText: Find a new home for the Soaked Totem in Loamm.
ObjectivesCompletionText: Find a niffen that likes this item.
